This is the source code for: http://gallery.caridy.name/

You must have git, NodeJS 0.2.1 and npm 0.2.0 installed

To use it, follow these simple steps:

    npm install yui3
    npm install yui3-gallery
    npm install yui3-2in3

    git clone git://github.com/caridy/yui3-gallery-dashboard.git

    cd yui3-gallery-dashboard

For a normal run:
    ./server.js

Visit: http://localhost:8001/

To use Spark: http://github.com/senchalabs/spark

Spark Config (config.js):

module.exports = {
    port: 8001,
    env: 'production',
    workers: 10
}

Install spark via:

    npm install spark
    spark

Visit: http://localhost:8001/
